title: Australian diary. No. 092
creator_credit: Jack S. Allan and Australian National Film Board
brief_description: The following items are featured in this interesting cinemagazine: Melbourne’s Royal Women’s Hospital provides mothers-to-be with all the facilities necessary for pre-natal and post-natal care; Newcastle’s State Dockyard is capable of building ships equal to the world’s best; Gundagai comes to life as the country town parades its pastoral wealth.
